{"tid":17422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防範意識弱　京大叔跳廣場舞交50性伴染愛滋","createTime":"2016-12-01T22:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T15:28:10.000Z","uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"210eef04d87fee2afeab89e9c3f584afabae1250","tid":17422,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:15:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRznvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=14400c8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 明日是世界愛滋病日。有北京傳媒報道，近年內地老年人感染愛滋病有上升趨勢，北京就有一名52歲男子透露跳廣場舞結交性伴侶，先後與50多名女子發生性行為，最終因此感染愛滋病。而聯合國愛滋病規劃署最新報告亦顯示，去年內地50歲以上愛滋病毒感染者達580萬人，創下歷史新高，反映內地中老年人對防範愛滋病的意識十分薄弱。<br />\n<br />\n李男向中心職員透露，自己此前曾有50多名性伴侶，均在跳廣場舞時結識。由於李男認為自己已有一定年紀，已失去使女性受孕的能力，因此發生性行為時也不戴安全套，但原來其中十幾個性伴侶已驗出患有愛滋病，而他自己最終亦感染愛滋。李男得知自己感染後，更因害怕「丟面子」，並未到正規醫院治療，因而延誤診治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkncn-20161130190220638-1130_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fbkncn-20161130190220638-1130_05011_001.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRznvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=06446246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkncn-20161130190220638-1130_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得咁多人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8902953077d37d465967dfc700de2a72dd87f6c","tid":17422,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:16:52.000Z","msg":"媾嬸廣場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3328c075122262a8e7b81af5bba3052eec49c4b","tid":17422,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:21:22.000Z","msg":"有時見到有好多後生跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c6708b629df2b62ce41e29c97df7d9c8c4e029","tid":17422,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:49:05.000Z","msg":"成班妹下妹下係到跳老舞擾民不特止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，性病仲要一籮籮，好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4019f7403dfdb9df13cab3c77cbffa25aec456da","tid":17422,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}